{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib"]]},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"typealias","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"roleHeading":"Type Alias","externalID":"s:4GLib22SourceFuncsPrepareFunca","title":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" = "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GSourceFuncsPrepareFunc","text":"GSourceFuncsPrepareFunc"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Called before all the file descriptors are polled. If the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"source can determine that it is ready here (without waiting for the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"results of the poll call) it should return "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":". It can also return","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timeout"},{"type":"text","text":" value which should be the maximum timeout (in milliseconds)"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"which should be passed to the poll call. The actual timeout used will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-1"},{"type":"text","text":" if all sources returned "},{"code":"-1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", or it will be the minimum of all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timeout"},{"type":"text","text":" values returned which were greater than or equal to "},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If the prepare function returns a timeout and the source also has a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"ready time set, then the lower of the two will be used."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since 2.36 this may be "},{"code":"NULL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", in which case the effect is as if the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"function always returns ","type":"text"},{"code":"FALSE","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" with a timeout of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-1"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/sourcefuncspreparefunc"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceFuncsPrepareFunc"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Checks the source for readiness."}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/SourceFuncsPrepareFunc":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/sourcefuncspreparefunc","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","fragments":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Checks the source for readiness."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"SourceFuncsPrepareFunc"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/glib","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","type":"topic"}}}